getPartialSenseKeyText

public String getPartialSenseKeyText()
Returns the sense key without included the head word portion. This version can be used to uniquely identify any word sense in the index file even if the key was constructed without the head word.

Returns:
Sense key text minus the last two fields (and the delimiter that separates them) that identify the head word.
